    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "specialists and support groups... i've done it all. i've tried every pill, every nerve block, every stupid little therapy. nothing works. it's just a loop of pain that never stops. sometimes i just sit here thinking about how much easier it would be if i could just... stop. if i could just find a way to reach that permanent stillness. it feels like the only real way to get actual peace.",
